                        <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18711120-43-offence-1 t18711120-geo-2"></join>Holloway Con<lb></lb>gregational Church</placeName>, and stealing two chalices and other articles, of <persName id="t18711120-name-218" type="victimName">
