                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Detective Sergeant</hi> 7). I was in Pentonville Road on 13th November—I assisted in taking Ward into custody—he was struggling with McMath and resisting—I found on him this large screw-driver, a candle, a few matches, and a knife.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Ward.</hi> I wish you would show these matches and knife. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> It is a small pocket knife, a candle, and three matches.</p>
